We re excited to share v3.0 StoryWave s biggest update ever! With this amazing update we ve redesigned much of the app to make it the perfect one stop shop for all video editing and social media creation needs! Powerful quick edit We ve added a quick and powerful editor called Quick Edit that allows you to do most of the common video tasks fast and with ease. Tasks like combine crop trim add text music and stunning effects and even animate photos and color correction for videos can now be done with Quick Edit. Create flows We now offer a variety of flows to start your project which will take you hand in hand and help you accomplish your video editing needs. Needs like Create Story Create Slideshow Add Music To Video Crop and Trim a Video Combine Videos and many more are now only a tap away. We ve also added 7 new themes and 9 animated text styles!

Welcome to v2.4.1 our first update of the 2020s! This version adds one of your most requested features you can now use your brand s logo as a watermark on the videos you create! We ve also made lots of user experience improvements and fixed some bugs. We wish you a wonderful 2020 with many amazing storywave videos!

Welcome to v2.4.0 our amazing Holiday update! What s new: 12 new themes! Including 6 Holiday themes and 6 beauty themes. Use live photos as videos if you select them from the Live Photos album. You can now duplicate your projects.
